{"tid":2489542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美智庫：拜登抗中強過川普","createTime":"2021-04-15T04:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T04:28:33.000Z","uid":52658,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3e7c2bf6248823eb8bedf92ae11b35c773c1dcb0","tid":2489542,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS7mZxyspFSu7LoRtEXLBnqZEt2xxug6qNECaLoJcWQC7?filename=gXqw5Ua.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXqw5Ua.png&h=50121ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美智庫一份報告指出，美國總統拜登的中國政策對金融機構的影響比川普時期更強。<br />\n<br />\n華盛頓智庫科文華盛頓研究集團（Cowen Washington Resear Group）在4月7日的一份報告中寫道：「我們相信拜登總統在應對中國方面對金融公司構成的風險要大於川普總統。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們認為拜登團隊比川普團隊在與中國的對抗中更有戰略性，更具多邊性也更加有效。」<br />\n<br />\n拜登就任總統後，延續川普政府對中國的強硬立場，並將中國稱作更自信的競爭者。上周四，拜登政府以國家安全為由，將11家中國科技公司列入「實體清單」。<br />\n<br />\n拜登強唔強過川普我唔知<br />\n但布林肯應該會強過蓬佩奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c494d7c2d024c7b220d7cd13d959340487c5472","tid":2489542,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:20:34.000Z","msg":"Cc toy 又話因為侵㗎咋"},{"pid":"8d926eeefc6b0fe7de4eb1f1ef15a30bef551cf5","tid":2489542,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:21:58.000Z","msg":"cctoy: China Joe! 上任後美國變中國省<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bff0186a1a733a29163ed724c8a247c130e89b8","tid":2489542,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:23:19.000Z","msg":"侵喺果陣烚熟狗頭<br />\n拜登上場就不吃這一套<br />\n<br />\n強係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog